==Amezruy==
[[Aɛmer Ubuyaḥya]] d yiwen umrabeḍ ,tezdeɣ tarwa-s tama n wasif ddaw Igures , di tgerwla mgal amnekcem afransis (1954) tefka d taddart 32 imeɣraṣen am [[Akli At Ṭayeb]] ,baya ak d fatima [[Tasaɛdit At Ṭayeb|At Ṭayeb]] ,ait tayeb djaafar ,  yamina ak dgmas lmajid ait tayeb,khider ait mouhoub, [[Muḥend Lɛerbi]] neɣ [[Busɛad Ujidan|Busɛad ak degmas idir Ujidan]]. mebla ma nasu andal amkran MHAND ATI MOUFFOK(MHEND ATH WAFTHIS).Syina mi yefra ṭrad, ulin atas imezdaɣ d asawen seg wasif mi yuɣen tiferkiwin ɣer taddart n [[At Mlal]] id yezgan s ufella n Igures (THAVOUCHEKIRT) .

